oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Taking the Backwork Out of Vet Work
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Hardman, W. David
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: animal practice
back
labor
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Having been in large animal practice for over twenty years I have out of necessity had to find ways to protect my back. If your back looks like mine the best method is to hire a young ambitious associate. Short of that we have found some ways to ease the burden on our backs.
